# 📖 Overview

This repository documents my practical journey in learning and implementing **Amazon Web Services (AWS)** through real-world projects and cloud deployment exercises.

The primary objective of this project is to understand cloud computing concepts, deploy secure virtual servers, configure cloud networking, host applications, and implement cybersecurity best practices within AWS.

The repository demonstrates the deployment, configuration, administration, and security of cloud-based environments using AWS services such as EC2, VPC, IAM, Security Groups, and Elastic IPs.

Throughout this project, I gained practical experience with Linux server management, Git version control, cloud networking, infrastructure security, application deployment, and troubleshooting.

